<p>克莱朵·诺沃斯（载体状态）<br />
由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3471238&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608124654" alt="breaddddd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3471238)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;">breaddddd</a></span>摄影</p>
